{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 121.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And on that plant, you could see prisoners of war from all-- every, probably every-- every country that was taking part in the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I remember some Canadians, I remember French, I remember English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Of course, they were treated a little bit differently then we.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We only met them at the-- at the camp, at the plant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were housed in separate camps and we were in different camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Of course, they were treated differently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In one particular case, I remember one winter-- one winter in 1944, we were standing and it was so bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The summer-- the winters were so harsh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Maybe they were-- they were harsher than we thought they were because we don't have any clothes, we don't have any food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were skin and bones, naturally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And one of them slipped me a-- a block of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I-- this was just like a unbelievable event.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I-- naturally, I put it in my pocket-- I put it in my pocket and I came back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this particular camp, I was with my brother together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were together and then we were separated and then we were together again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this [GERMAN], we were together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came back to the camp and I-- he was in a different column, and I was in a different barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, guess what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You'll never believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A guy just slipped me so nobody should see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were standing near a fire to warm ourselves up in the-- in the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like a whole city there, they-- they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, we were well-watched and well-guarded, but within the working area, we were free to move.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
